data.description: !!!BACK ON MARKET and OFFERING A 10K SELLER CREDIT FOR RATE BUY-DOWN!!! This STUNNING home has all the bells and whistles in nearly 3200 sq ft of living space! This FORMER MODEL HOME, the "Santina" model, features many designer touches including TRAY CEILINGS, DECORATIVE MOLDINGS and many other great features. Large great room, formal dining and a large kitchen make this home PERFECT FOR ENTERTAINING! Soaring tall ceilings meet you the moment you walk in the door! The kitchen has abundant 42" cabinetry, granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry, island and breakfast nook. Relaxing master retreat features an oversized bedroom with tray ceiling, huge walk-in closet and a luxury bathroom with garden tub, dual sinks and glass shower. Generously sized bedrooms and dual sinks in the second full bath will accommodate everyone. The big laundry room is great for large families. Check out the garage! It's an extended 3 CAR PLUS - lots of room for storage and larger vehicles. Covered lanai and fenced yard. It has it all! Ridge Crest is one of the Tampa Bay area's best kept secrets with beautiful homes, landscape, and easy access to Tampa, MacDill AFB, I-75 and I-4. Schedule a private showing today!
